('finance-sales-marketing-operations-metrics', 'grp-business-fundamentals', 3, 'topic', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Core Business Metrics', 'Learn common metrics across finance, sales, marketing, product, customer support, operations, and HR.', 'This node builds practical BI analyst capability in core business metrics.', 'side', 'ph-bi-foundations', 1, 203, 3, 'beginner', 3, NULL, NULL, '{"source": "roadmap.sh/bi-analyst", "parentGroup": "grp-business-fundamentals"}'::jsonb, true, true, '["Explain Core Business Metrics through business question, metric definition, data evidence, and stakeholder communication.", "Apply Core Business Metrics in a realistic business intelligence task.", "Identify trade-offs, risks, debugging signals, or quality checks related to the topic."]'::jsonb, '["Create or update notes explaining Core Business Metrics with a concrete example.", "Use the topic to produce a metric note, report sketch, dashboard mockup, or analysis artifact.", "Record at least two decisions, risks, or validation checks that prove applied understanding."]'::jsonb),
