('grp-interview-readiness', 'ph-portfolio-career', 1420, 'choice_group', NULL, 'complete_all', NULL, 'BI Interview Readiness', 'Group related options around BI Interview Readiness so learners can complete the required selection model without changing the main phase structure.', 'This node builds practical BI analyst capability in bi interview readiness.', 'side', 'ph-portfolio-career', 14, 20, 2, 'advanced', 1420, NULL, NULL, '{"selectionType": "complete_all", "source": "roadmap.sh/bi-analyst"}'::jsonb, true, false, '["Compare the options or grouped topics inside BI Interview Readiness.", "Select or complete the required children according to the group rule.", "Explain how the selected work supports practical business intelligence readiness."]'::jsonb, '["Complete the required number of child nodes for this group.", "Document why the selected options fit the learner''s target direction or project needs.", "Confirm that required child projects or topics have reviewable evidence."]'::jsonb),
